The Ministry of Health has announced that 18 more patients have died of the newÂ coronavirus in the past 24 hours, increasing the overall death toll to 456. In a press briefing on Wednesday, Health Chief Administrative Secretary Mercy Mwangangi confirmed 679 new cases of Covid-19 infection, raising the total number of infections to 28,104. Dr Mwangangi said 743 more patients recovered from Covid-19 taking the recoveries tally to 14, 610. She added that so far 369,091 Covid-19 tests have been taken across the country. More follows.